'''珀西·威廉姆斯·布里奇曼'''（{{lang-en|Percy Williams Bridgman}}，{{bd|1882年|4月21日|1961年|8月20日|B}}），[[美国|美国]][[物理学家|物理学家]]，因他在高壓物理方面的貢獻，1946年获得[[诺贝尔物理学奖|诺贝尔物理学奖]]。布里奇曼對[[科學方法|科學方法]]及[[科學哲學|科學哲學]]的一些觀點有相當廣泛的著述。<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1063/1.3057180 | title = Percy W. Bridgman | journal = Physics Today | volume = 14 | issue = 10 | pages = 78 | year = 1961 | pmid =  | pmc = }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Bridgman | first1 = P. | title = A Complete Collection of Thermodynamic Formulas | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_physical-review_1914-04_3_4/page/273 | doi = 10.1103/PhysRev.3.273 | journal = Physical Review | volume = 3 | issue = 4 | pages = 273–281 | year = 1914 | pmid =  | pmc = |bibcode = 1914PhRv....3..273B }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Bridgman | first1 = P. W. | title = Probability, Logic, and ESP | doi = 10.1126/science.123.3184.15 | journal = Science | volume = 123 | issue = 3184 | pages = 15–17 | year = 1956 | pmid =  13281470| pmc = |bibcode = 1956Sci...123...15B }}</ref>晚年因罹患癌症，飲彈自殺。

